node.text:
Pressure makes diamonds ♦️ ✍🏾💯🌊🏄🏾‍♂️💎

So many people wana criticize this  first movement when they could just ASK soooo lol First exercise is a partial lateral raise, used to build solid muscle fibers in the delt, the range of motion is about 3-4 inches which allows you to go heavy in weight, I started the exercise using 70lbs and moved up 10lbs each set to 100lbs..these are the first movement after warming up the delts with traditional side lateral raises✍🏾🏄🏾‍♂️

But aye, STAY READY, STAY WAVY, period.✍🏾💯🌊🏄🏾‍♂️💎

node.text:
My team getting stronger and stronger! We just added my boy Chiro doctor  @fitforlifedoc to the squad to help keep us in line and make sure everything is moving the way it should! We are going to be getting weekly adjustments as we prepare to battle and defend the title this year at the ⭕️💪🏾 If you’re in the Miami area and in need of Chiropractic therapy make sure to hit up @fitforlifedoc! He competes also so he has a completely different prospective and approach when it comes to chiro therapy! HE GETS IT💯 let’s work✍🏾🌊🏄🏾‍♂️💎
